room_title: Escape room "No Vacancy" by Haunting Productions in Portland
room_description: On a stormy night, you take refuge inside an inviting hotel down a dark alley. Once inside, you realize you are trapped within a multi-room trap with only 60 minutes to escape. Try to crack the code of the dimensional shifting rooms before you're lost to another world forever. With a working elevator and hidden doors as part of the room, No Vacancy is the most technologically advanced and challenging room in Portland, OR.
